{"tid":1118242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"於布吉島擅自建海上屋 夫妻 2 人恐面臨死刑","createTime":"2019-04-21T09:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T12:08:48.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b7b9005faf8ca2a54340e4192ec3ce2ccc06e4","tid":1118242,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"泰國渡假勝地布吉島有不少休閑渡假的 Villas ，近年更越開越多 pool access 的別墅房，房間直接對著泳池甚至大海，想游泳隨時都能從房間直接跳下去，環境優美，不少港人都喜歡放假時去 Relax 一下。但不知大家有否想過也建一間在海上的別墅呢？一名美國商人與泰藉妻子，疑在布吉島附近的海域建了一間海上房屋，卻被泰國政府發現並指夫婦二人侵犯了國家主權，一經定罪，可能會面臨死刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2330000/2331674/sea02_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2330000%2F2331674%2Fsea02_600.JPG&h=4a1e7701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據外國媒體報道，該名美國商人 Chad Andrew Elwartowski 和泰籍伴侶 Nadia 在布吉島附近海域約 12 海里處興建了一間海上房屋，兩人更曾於別墅內生活過數周，但卻被泰國政府最近一次的巡邏發現了該間別墅，被政府控告二人在未取得政府的同意下，在泰國的領海上私自興建房屋，觸犯泰國刑法第 119 條。此舉侵犯了泰國領士的主權完整性，根據泰國法律，可將二人判處無期徒刑，甚至死刑。<br />\n<br />\n但有知情人士指，該房屋並不是夫妻二人所興建的，他們只是在屋內居住過數周而已。有傳該間海上房屋，是由提倡在國際水域建造房屋而不受國家法律約束的團體「海上家園(Seasteading) 」所興建的。對此，「海上家園」的建造商 （Ocean Builders）則回應指，該房屋位於國際水域，實屬合法，而涉事的夫婦目前情況安全，他們亦希望可以透過外交方式與泰國政府解決此次事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2330000/2331674/sea01_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2330000%2F2331674%2Fsea01_600.JPG&h=3d80a5f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9c22a89fc4b2f6972eee670bd5ee8ac459acb29","tid":1118242,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:53:17.000Z","msg":"整間屋使唔使咁誇張"},{"pid":"77253c6eae3e93b3d4ca0d466404398391b616ab","tid":1118242,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9c22a89fc4b2f6972eee670bd5ee8ac459acb29","tid":1118242,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:53:17.000Z","msg":"整間屋使唔使咁誇張"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:49:01.000Z","msg":"死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a939a5f536cd68853d64e3a6ebed998ad159b2","tid":1118242,"uid":84668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"MGSV<br />\n<br />\nMother base<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f328aea076c0e1b39494373381286fb8111157","tid":1118242,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77253c6eae3e93b3d4ca0d466404398391b616ab","tid":1118242,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9c22a89fc4b2f6972eee670bd5ee8ac459acb29","tid":1118242,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:53:17.000Z","msg":"整間屋使唔使咁誇張"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:49:01.000Z","msg":"死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"可以即場射殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}